in Staja Number 84-F

465
00:47:47,917 --> 00:47:51,446
among smelly perverts
and hardened prestoopniks.

466
00:47:51,756 --> 00:47:55,556
The shock sending my dada beating
his bruised and krovvy rookers

467
00:47:55,786 --> 00:47:58,126
against unfair Bog
in His Heaven.

468
00:47:58,396 --> 00:48:01,586
And my mum boo-hoo-hooing
in her mother's grief

469
00:48:01,826 --> 00:48:04,226
at her only child
and son of her bosom

470
00:48:04,496 --> 00:48:07,095
like, letting everybody down
real horror show.

471
00:48:07,335 --> 00:48:10,235
Morning.
One up from Thames, mister.

472
00:48:11,275 --> 00:48:12,895
Right! Open up the cell!

473
00:48:13,135 --> 00:48:14,575
Yes, sir.

474
00:48:30,854 --> 00:48:33,124
Here are the prisoner's
committal forms.

475
00:48:33,354 --> 00:48:34,844
Thank you, mister.

476
00:48:36,493 --> 00:48:39,193
- Name?
- Alexander DeLarge.

477
00:48:39,463 --> 00:48:41,363
You are now in
H.M. Prison Parkmoor.

478
00:48:41,663 --> 00:48:45,193
From this moment, you will address
all prison officers as "sir"

479
00:48:45,433 --> 00:48:46,263
Name?

480
00:48:46,473 --> 00:48:48,833
Alexander DeLarge, sir.

481
00:48:49,143 --> 00:48:50,133
Sentence?

482
00:48:50,443 --> 00:48:51,602
14 years, sir.

483
00:48:51,842 --> 00:48:52,702
Crime?

484
00:48:52,972 --> 00:48:54,102
Murder, sir.

485
00:48:54,382 --> 00:48:57,312
Right.
Take the cuffs off him, mister.

486
00:49:08,621 --> 00:49:11,021
You are now 655321.

487
00:49:11,291 --> 00:49:14,521
It is your duty
to memorize that number.

488
00:49:14,801 --> 00:49:16,821
Thank you, mister. Well done.

489
00:49:17,071 --> 00:49:18,791
- Thank you.
- Let the officer out.

490
00:49:23,070 --> 00:49:25,560
All right, empty your pockets.

491
00:49:29,310 --> 00:49:32,400
Are you able to see the white line
painted on the floor

492
00:49:32,680 --> 00:49:34,010
directly behind you

493
00:49:34,220 --> 00:49:35,580
655321?

494
00:49:38,089 --> 00:49:39,519
Then your toes belong

495
00:49:39,749 --> 00:49:41,719
on the other side of it!

496
00:49:48,759 --> 00:49:50,419
- Yes, sir.
- Right.

497
00:49:50,869 --> 00:49:52,199
Carry on.

498
00:49:57,068 --> 00:49:57,998
Pick that up

499
00:49:58,238 --> 00:50:00,998
and put it down properly.

500
00:50:11,787 --> 00:50:13,847
One half-bar of chocolate.

501
00:50:15,857 --> 00:50:18,757
One bunch of keys
